Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: California's Proposition 15
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z9b56
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 May 1976
Voters in California asked to back Proposition 15 which could limit the use of nuclear power and lead to a further energy crisis. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less